        "rule": "Users must be able to view reports of their usage data",
        "testable_assertion": "UNTESTABLE as stated — 'usage' is undefined. Blocked on Bird defining which metrics constitute 'usage'. Shaq should stub a UsageMetrics interface that can be swapped once defined."
      },
      {
        "rule": "Reports must be downloadable",
        "testable_assertion": "Given a generated report, when the user requests download, then a file is returned with Content-Disposition: attachment header. Format TBD — Bird did not specify; MJ assumed CSV and PDF."
      },
      {
        "rule": "Users must be able to filter reports by time period",
        "testable_assertion": "Given a report request with a time range, when the report is generated, then only data within that range is included. Note: Bird said 'time period' — could mean free-range start/end dates OR preset windows (last 7d, 30d, 90d). MJ assumed start_date/end_date parameters."
